ile:Plainstage.svg|20px|alt=|link=]] || Plain stage|| {{flagathlete|[[Gustave Garrigou]]|FRA}} || {{flagathlete|[[Lucien Petit-Breton]]|FRA}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1907 Tour de France, Stage 8 to Stage 14#Stage 13|13]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1 August || [[Brest, France|Brest]] to [[Caen]]\n| {{convert|415|km|mi|abbr=on}} || [[File:Plainstage.svg|20px|alt=|link=]] || Plain stage|| {{flagathlete|[[Emile Georget]]|FRA}} || {{flagathlete|[[Lucien Petit-Breton]]|FRA}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1907 Tour de France, Stage 8 to Stage 14#Stage 14|14]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 4 August || [[Caen]] to [[Paris]]\n| {{convert|251|km|mi|abbr=on}} || [[File:Plainstage.svg|20px|alt=|link=]] || Plain stage|| {{flagathlete|[[Georges Passerieu]]|FRA}} || {{flagathlete|[[Lucien Petit-Breton]]|FRA}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"| Total\n| colspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center\"| {{convert|4488|km|0|abbr=on}}{{sfn|Augendre|2016|p=108}}\n|}\n\n===General classification===\n\nAlthough 110 riders were on the starting list, 17 did not show up, so the race started with 93 cyclists. At the end of the Tour de France, 33 cyclists remained.<ref name=\"mdc1907\" />\nThe cyclists officially were not grouped in teams; some cyclists had the same sponsor, even though they were not allowed to work together.{{sfn|Thompson|2006|p=36}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:44em; margin-bottom:0;\"\n|+ Final general classification (1\u201310)<ref name=\"mdc1907\"/><ref name=\"elm\">{{cite web|url=http://hemeroteca-paginas.mundodeportivo.com/EMD02/HEM/1907/08/08/MD19070808-006.pdf|title=Le Tour de France|date=8 August 1907|page=6|language=Spanish|work=[[Mundo Deportivo]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191006131100/http://hemeroteca-paginas.mundodeportivo.com/EMD02/HEM/1907/08/08/MD19070808-006.pdf|archive-date=6 October 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Rank!! scope=\"col\" | Rider!! scope=\"col\" | Sponsor!! scope=